Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:59.47,ED-JP,,0,25,75,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}あの日、貸してもらった　始まりは　さくらいろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:31.57,ED-JP,,0,25,75,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}鉛筆で描いてみた校舎裏の木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:39.04,ED-JP,,0,25,75,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}失くしたまま忘れてた色で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:46.93,ED-JP,,0,25,75,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}声を掛けてくれた君が埋めた平行線を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:51.59,ED-JP,,0,25,75,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}なぞっては思い出してた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:59.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}冬が過ぎてまた巡ってる　未完成だったぼくの心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:08.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}うつむいて嘘ついて　焦ってばかりでは答えは見えないと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:14.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}教えてくれたよ　いつかは　さくらいろに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:21.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あれから、それから　ぼくら風になった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:28.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}気まぐれなんかじゃなくて特別な色だから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:34.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}いまから、これから(ずっと)　続くこのキャンバスに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:38.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}覚えていたいフィクサチーフで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}始まりは　さくらいろ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.83,0:07:52.45,ED-CH,,0,25,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}從那天起 在那以後 我們化作風
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.45,0:07:59.47,ED-CH,,0,25,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}那天你給我的起點 是櫻花的顏色
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.86,0:08:31.57,ED-CH,,0,25,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}用鉛筆畫下校園後庭的樹
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.57,0:08:39.04,ED-CH,,0,25,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}遺失之後 連顏色也忘記
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.13,0:08:46.93,ED-CH,,0,25,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}你向我搭話 埋下了一對平行線
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.93,0:08:51.59,ED-CH,,0,25,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3}沿著它勾畫 喚醒了我的回憶
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.59,0:08:59.02,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}冬天去又來 我的內心依然沒有準備好
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.02,0:09:08.86,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}低下頭 言不由衷 只在心裡著急是找不到答案的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.86,0:09:14.72,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}是你點醒了我 終將化為櫻色
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.04,0:09:21.83,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}從那天起 在那以後 我們化作風
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.83,0:09:28.13,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}這並非心血來潮 而是特別的色彩
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.13,0:09:34.64,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}從今天起 一直往後 無限延續的畫布上
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.64,0:09:38.00,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}想要用固定劑 定格每一個瞬間
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.64,ED-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\an2}我們起始於櫻花的顏色
Comment: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------OP「Now On Air」----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の続きをリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえますか？未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:56.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて届ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:05.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}はじまりのナンバー　夢にとどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}平坦な道　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:13.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:16.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:27.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:33.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:47.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:09.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:13.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的續集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}會聽到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:56.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:05.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的開場曲 飛向夢想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是尋找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:13.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只會讓我厭倦前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:16.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去實現 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想為何會因為這隻手改變形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:27.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}請告訴我 還要努力多久才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:33.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾經只能仰視理想的我 已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:47.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊 直抵更遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣賞美景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追隨直覺活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:09.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到無法發聲為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:13.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都會一直為你開口
Comment: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:26.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:54.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:23:00.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:10.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:27.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:26.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 為什麼讓我如此煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}總是搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其實那麼喜歡你 卻言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合適的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我們四目相對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:54.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:23:00.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:10.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定會接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}願這首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以讓世界稍微改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:27.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然後與你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多公分的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填滿
Comment: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.85,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
